    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mostly metal parts of a single-reed instrument used to keep the reed in place against the mouthpiece, without obstructing its vibrations when played.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
